Install Vagrant Tool:
--------------------------------------------------------
(This two commands can helps to install the Vagrant Tool in any of the mac)

brew tap hashicorp/tap
brew install hashicorp/tap/hashicorp-vagrant



Vagrant Tool box helps to get any kind of images from the " https://app.vagrantup.com/boxes/search ".

we can use the images to create the OS and also we use this in the Vagrantfile. 
